    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. The CFD model is deemed credible for its intended use: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The primary claim (RH = 0.87 < 1.0) satisfies the pre-specified regulatory acceptance criterion. The credibility assessment package is accepted for inclusion in the 510(k) submission dossier.",
